Package com.ibm.fhir.cli

Enum OptionNames

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<OptionNames>
      • com.ibm.fhir.cli.OptionNames
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<OptionNames>
    public enum OptionNames
extends Enum<OptionNames>
    This enum defines each of the command-line options, including the long name, short name, description and an optional "argName" field for options which take an additional argument.
